    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a well-maintained E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver linear power with a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain provides an engaging, tactile experience. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive throttle actuator service and a Blackstone oil analysis confirming healthy rod bearing wear. The hydraulic steering rack offers exceptional feedback, unencumbered by modern electronic interference. This specimen shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age but remains mechanically robust and optimized for spirited performance.",
